				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">In loadspc.asm there are two sections that I think are SPC codes, namely spc700_init_code and spc700_fasl_code. So you'd have to extend them so they listen to changes on the four ports? </div>
<br />Those are only used during the uploading process. spc700_fasl_code is overwritten when spc700_init_code executes, and spc700_init_code is (in most cases) overwritten once the song starts playing.</div>

